Are you a finance professional with a passion for delivering insightful reporting, leveraging advanced analytical tools and driving business performance? Diploma Qualification in Accounting, Finance, Commerce or business-related discipline with sound knowledge and practical application of accounting standards and financial management practices.
Professional Accounting Qualification (CA/CPA) or working towards
